riscv: Add SiPeed MAIX BiT board device tree

Add the device tree sipeed_maix_bit.dts for the SiPeed MAIX BiT and
MAIX BiTm boards. This device tree enables LEDs, gpio, i2c and spi/mmc
SD card devices.

